<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Filter_Compress can compress complete directories but it would be handy if it could compress an arbitrary user defined array of files.</p>

<p>eg:</p>

<p>$filter = new Zend_Filter_Compress(array(
    'adapter' =&gt; 'Zip',
    'options' =&gt; array(
        'archive' =&gt; 'filename.zip'
    ),
));</p>

<p>$compressed = $filter-&gt;filter(array('file1', 'file4', 'file5'));</p>

    </div>
